/Obelisk%20feature%20image.png?imwidth=320" alt="Obelisk in garden " fetchpriority="low" loading="lazy" height="500" width="800" decoding="async"/></picture></figure><div class="mt-2 text-ellipsis-row-3 md:text-base md:leading-6">Garden obelisks: the best plant supports for your garden</div></div></a><a href="/buyers-guide/promotions/win-a-burgon-and-ball-x-sophie-conran-tool-bundle/"><div><figure class="relative h-0 pb-[62.5%]"><picture><img class="block h-[100%] w-[100%] opacity-1 transition-opacity absolute top-0" src="/_gatsby/file/fe55586d1a4621621f5c3a198ce9b9c8/Sophie%20conran%20tool%20bundle.png?imwidth=320" alt="Sophie Conran x Burgon &amp; Ball tool bundle " fetchpriority="low" loading="lazy" height="500" width="800" decoding="async"/></picture></figure><div class="mt-2 text-ellipsis-row-3 md:text-base md:leading-6">WIN a Burgon &amp; Ball x Sophie Conran tool bundle worth 155</div></div></a><a href="/buyers-guide/promotions/a-unique-range-of-coir-pots-for-the-eco-conscious-grower-from-coirproducts/"><div><figure class="relative h-0 pb-[62.5%]"><picture><img class="block h-[100%] w-[100%] opacity-1 transition-opacity absolute top-0" src="/_gatsby/file/78dc8fb1ff335a74be36c88a88b09a4d/CoirProducts.png?imwidth=320" alt="CoirProducts" fetchpriority="low" loading="lazy" height="500" width="800" decoding="async"/></picture></figure><div class="mt-2 text-ellipsis-row-3 md:text-base md:leading-6">A unique range of coir pots for the eco-conscious grower from CoirProducts</div></div></a><a href="/buyers-guide/our-guide-to-the-best-water-butts/"><div><figure class="relative h-0 pb-[62.5%]"><picture><img class="block h-[100%] w-[100%] opacity-1 transition-opacity absolute top-0" src="/_gatsby/file/6a29de389bd18ef124c718bc50cd633b/Water%20butt.png?imwidth=320" alt="Galvanised steel water butt" fetchpriority="low" loading="lazy" height="500" width="800" decoding="async"/></picture></figure><div class="mt-2 text-ellipsis-row-3 md:text-base md:leading-6">Our guide to eig